- The integer array parameter `inventory` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `inventory` length must be between 1 and 10^5.
- Each element in the integer array parameter `inventory` must be between 1 and 10^9.
- The integer parameter `orders` must be between 1 and the sum of all elements in the integer array parameter `inventory`, or 10^9, whichever is smaller.
- The integer result is the maximum total value that can be attained after selling the specified number of colored balls.